{
  "stem": "1684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first deportation was in three-- in three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then there was another day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I had nothing to do with the other day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the other day, they came to my husband's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my husband, he-- on his [INAUDIBLE] on his walking paper, he had like-- it said businessman, because he was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had a big business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so when he came to the registration, he saw somebody getting a little K, and there was a little-- by the registration, there was a big seal and a small seal.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, he saw somebody getting the small seal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this guy asked something, so the gestapo hit him over the head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what my husband told me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he said, I'm not a business-- oh, he said, you're a businessman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He wanted to take the small seal to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said, no I'm not a businessman anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now I'm a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My husband paid a locksmith to get employed by him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he had already [INAUDIBLE] with the locksmith.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So when he came to that, he said, I am now a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took the big seal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had another paper, his identification, with his name and his picture on it and his age on it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put that in too, and he gave him two seals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had the two seals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was in my-- in my husband's apartment, it was already the third deportation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, these gestapo people, they came in, and they never-- they never, you know, knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came with the big boots, and they just knocked the door in or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were always a little drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had the bayonet, you know, with-- with them, and the guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
